					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td width=200 bgcolor=#bbbbbb valign=top>
						<font face=helvetica size=-1>
						Consider doing a full vis and radiosity compile from time to time as your map grows. Lighting can take a lot of tweaking, and it's easier to get sections of your map
done and behind you than try to fix the whole thing at the end. Don't use the -ambient						</font>
